Usage: createSpecialDrcRegion [-help] [-extendOuterX <float>]
                              [-extendOuterY <float>] [-extendX <float>]
                              [-extendY <float>] [-insts <string>]
                              -layer <string>

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
-extendOuterX <float>           # expand the routing blockage in X direction.
                                # (float, optional)
-extendOuterY <float>           # expand the routing blockage in X direction.
                                # (float, optional)
-extendX <float>                # expand the instnace boudary to cut routing
                                # blockage in X direction. (float, optional)
-extendY <float>                # expand the instnace boudary to cut routing
                                # blockage in Y direction. (float, optional)
-insts <string>                 # inst names needed be cut out
                                # (string, optional)
-layer <string>                 # the layer names which we will create the
                                # routing blockage on it. (string, required)